Poetry - Environment Inspection

Manage dependencies in your Python project with [prgm]poetry[/prgm]. Use the [prgm]env[/prgm] subcommand to explore the [prgm]venv[/prgm].

Environment information

$ [prgm]poetry env info[/prgm]                    # Show environment information
$ [prgm]poetry env activate[/prgm]                # Activate virtualenv

Configuring virtualenv location

$ [prgm]poetry config[/prgm] [arg-value]virtualenvs.in-project[/arg-value] [arg-value]true[/arg-value]
